dct_title_s: Carte de la Coôte de Peágu :
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:1,050,000 (E 94°00'00"--E 97°56'00"/N 17°20'00"--N 14°20'00"). Relief shown pictorially. Depths shown by soundings. Numbered as Plate 35, likely from: Le Neptune oriental, dedie au roi / par M. d'Apres de Mannevillette, 1775. Text in French.
Ames Library of South Asia Maps
